com.xtructure.xutil
Enum ValueType

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<ValueType>
      com.xtructure.xutil.ValueType
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ValueType>
public enum ValueType
extends java.lang.Enum<ValueType>

The Enum ValueType. ValueType enumerates the different types of values that can be identified by XValIds, and thus what types can be used with ValueMap.

Author:
Luis Guimbarda
